{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/\u6807\u98981\uff08\u82f1\uff09.png?t=1737545996\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The liquid form</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The liquid form possesses the ability to jump, swim in water, and recover health points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/1_\u6c34\u5f62\u6001\u79fb\u52a8.gif?t=1737545996\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The solid form</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The solid form has the ability to roll, float in water, break through obstacles, and activate mechanisms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/2_\u51b0\u5f62\u6001\u6eda\u52a8.gif?t=1737545996\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The steam form</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The steam form grants the ability to fly, but it is more challenging to control. Contact with obstacles and walls can result in taking damage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/3_\u6c7d\u5f62\u6001\u98de\u884c.gif?t=1737545996\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Form transformations</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cross obstacles through transforming three forms , such as switching from steam to solid form at high altitude and crashing into obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/4_\u4e09\u6001\u53d8\u6362\u65b0.gif?t=1737545996\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/\u6807\u98982\uff08\u82f1\uff09.png?t=1737545996\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Push box</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/5_\u63a8\u7bb1\u5b50.gif?t=1737545996\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Electrical puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/6_\u7535\u5b66\u89e3\u8c1c.gif?t=1737545996\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Optical Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/7_\u5149\u5b66\u89e3\u8c1c.gif?t=1737545996\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/\u6807\u98983\uff08\u82f1\uff09.png?t=1737545996\" />With simple editing of vertices, you can create terrain of various shapes, and all platforms, obstacles, and mechanisms can be freely placed. Whether the map you want to design is a difficult operation or a brain burning puzzle, everything is designed by you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At present, there are over 2000 maps  made by\u00a0 players in the game. The map you created will be shared with all PC and mobile players worldwide, let's create a water-based world together!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/8_\u5730\u56fe\u5de5\u574a.gif?t=1737545996\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/\u6807\u98984\uff08\u82f1\uff09.png?t=1737545996\" />Multiplayer mode allows you to collaborate with friends and enjoy more fun. Hurry up an